text: Woombup is a remote civil parish of Yantara County in far North West New South Wales, located at 30°12′49″S 142°32′44″E. The Geography, of the parish is mostly the flat, arid landscape of the Channel Country. The parish has a Köppen climate classification of BWh (Hot desert) (direct: Final Revised Paper). The nearest town is Tibooburra to the north west, which is on the Silver City Highway and lies south of the Sturt National Park. ==References== Category:Parishes of Yantara County Category:Far West (New South Wales)
title: Parish of Woombup
